Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:41.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:57.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:03.06,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.53,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:11.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:18.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:28.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:34.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:41.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:48.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:56.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:01.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hitchhiking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To Nekomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:41.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm going to be a\ncollege student, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's Honshu....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei's there somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be docking soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:03.87,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! A Blessing in Every Bargain?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:10.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Three days to go before I get paid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:23.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, my day off...\nand I'm totally strapped for cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:29.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you know how chaotic it's been\never since we met, Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:34.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I rather like the idea of\ntaking it easy once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure... you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it is kinda nice,\nsitting here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there is just one small problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:58.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we do something about this,\nI won't be able to cook for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:03.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I can go\nwithout eating for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:08.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just get a job that pays by the day\ntomorrow. We'll make it through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:12.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Why don't you\nlet me take care of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Take care of... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you conjure up money, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:22.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. But I have a spell that will\nbring good fortune to you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here is a wandering soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Provide the soul that resides here\nwith the sustenance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:37.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he needs to live at least until\nthe sun has risen and set three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, we have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:52.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me if there's a\NKeiichi Morisato living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:05.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here to see Keiichi, he's\nright inside... so please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:11.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi... you mean, Keiichi Morisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:15.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy? Who's that at the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Keiichi, we have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,M-Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:34.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kei's kid sister.\NMy name's Megumi Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well! To think you've come\nall this way to pay us a visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, now...{\i0}\NAren't you supposed to be in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:47.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought you'd be able\nto rent a great house like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a really long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but you're living\nwith such a gorgeous lady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's {\i1}so{\i0} not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:59.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't anyone ever teach you to have\na shred of respect for your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kei... aren't you\ngoing to introduce us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for not\nintroducing myself sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:12.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was sent here from the Goddess\NHelp Line, and my name is Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess... Help... Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:21.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What she means is...\nshe works for a volunteer group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So her community service\nincludes going out with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up! Stop asking\nthose nosy questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:32.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have a contract\nwith Mister Keiichi Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:36.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...according to which I shall\nbe by his side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:39.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite a character, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Megumi...\NWhat the heck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to get accepted to\na college in the Kanto area!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:01.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to pay you a visit while I\nwas here looking for an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:05.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What about those two?\NWeren't they opposed to your applying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to a college on the mainland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it just goes to show\nhow much they trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But they were so against\nmy applying to college here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get back in time\nfor graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was planning to find\na place today and go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But since you've got plenty of room,\nI guess I can stay for a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and take my time looking\nfor the right apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:35.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't you\njust settle down here with Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:40.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I can't find a place I like,\nthat might be an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:46.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously think you'd have fun\nat college living with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be young again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:52.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to spend it without\nanyone breathing down your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell I was just kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:08:01.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I was around, it would\njust kinda spoil things, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:05.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're talking about me,\nI have no problem whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:11.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi made the decision to come\nover here and be independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:16.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So let's do everything we can to\nhelp her find her own apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a caring\nolder brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:29.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better find her a place before\nshe finds out who Belldandy really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:33.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get romantic with her\nwhen there's no one else around...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:36.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...no way is Megumi going\nto stick around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, it's only until\nyou find your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, you're the man! Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this is my way of saying thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, how impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:59.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be craving\nsome home cooking by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I brought all this from Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did, did you?\NMan, you really saved the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money\nfor food right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I can get you\nto help me out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:17.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about this city, so\nI'm actually at a loss about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can just leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:24.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of apartment\ndo you have in mind, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, something like this, more or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,2 six-mat rooms at the very least?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Private bathroom... Kitchen...\nan absolute must!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:36.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A southeast-facing room with\nplenty of sunlight... Non-negotiable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No more than a 10-minute walk\nto the nearest train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Built within the last 5 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For less than 15,000 yen a month?{\i0}\NBuilt within the last 5 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For less than 15,000 yen a month?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:48.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if worst comes to worst,\nI'm willing to go up to 20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:10:01.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you... you really don't\nhave a clue, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say I'm going to\ngive you a dose of reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:24.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The best you can possibly do with your\npitiful budget is a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A room that stinks of testosterone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a very unique room.{\i0}\NA room that stinks of testosterone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:35.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I let half of my precious youth go down\nthe drain, jerked around by the seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could survive\na living hell like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:42.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A full-on workout, 100 push-ups,\N100 squats per leg every morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:45.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:50.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say happened to\nhalf of your precious youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Belldandy, who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These are the members\nof the NIT Auto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:00.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, you've\nreally got some balls...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not once, but twice, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:08.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You dare to bring women into our\nmale sanctuary, so laden with tradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no, you've got it all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:15.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but you've reviled this\nsacred ground by calling it a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:21.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're aware of the\nsheer enormity of such crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Out you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:39.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, you sure have some colorful seniors\nrunning this club of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! You see where\nI'm coming from now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard enough in Hokkaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But finding a place to live here\nis a freaking nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen, don't let it\nget you down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:01.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha! Of course I checked out\nthe market before coming over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:05.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you never know where you might\nfind a really great bargain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:11.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if we just look hard enough, I'm sure\nthat we'll find a lovely place for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:18.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so maybe I wasn't being realistic,\nthinking I'd find a place in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:22.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But just watch me! Tomorrow\nI'm really going to pound the pavement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll do whatever\nwe can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Won't we, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:33.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it's\ngoing to be that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:52.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, it's been ages since I\nlast got to hang out with you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, could you get real for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:13:00.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got today and tomorrow.\NYou need to get a grip on yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I find a nice apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:07.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we find someplace that\nmeets all of your requirements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:12.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I certainly hope so, too...\nfor god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Real Estate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Property, Buildings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we do not\nhave anything available.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rentals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you really think we'd have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:49.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Houmei Realty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:57.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Property, Homes, Apartments{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the sunlight...\nI can live without it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have some tea with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:25.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Megumi.\nIt's about your apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The way things are going, it doesn't look\nlikely that we'll find the kind of place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, you don't have\nto worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't find my ideal apartment,\nall I have to do is modify my wish list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:43.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make poor\NKei suffer any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:49.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're thinking, you're going\nto ask him to let me live here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:54.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that, it's only\ngoing to disappoint Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it would disappoint\nhim to have to live with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:07.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's because you're so\nconsiderate that Kei fell for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it wear you out to\nbe that way all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what more could you expect\nfrom the Goddess Help Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:21.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we've got a long day\ntomorrow, so I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:24.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, good night, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look after Kei for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:40.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O dwelling that I seek,\nyou are at rest somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please reveal your resting-place to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I shall release you\nfrom your slumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:57.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If angels and goddesses really do exist,\nI wonder if they're just like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Real Estate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:07.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we've got one. An apartment\nthat meets all your requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful, isn't it, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:11.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:16.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think you should pass on it.{\i0}\NAll right! This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:21.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Built 4 years ago. Has its own\nbathroom, 2 six-mat rooms and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a 4-mat-sized kitchen. A 10-minute\nwalk to the nearest train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has a room facing the southwest.\nIt's on the 1st floor of a 2-story complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:33.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The rent's 20,000 yen a month!\nIt matches my wish list exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:37.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kei, I want to\ntake a look inside right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen? A+!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom? A+!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Both rooms? A+!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sold, I'm taking this apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:03.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it sure is a steal\nat 20,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:07.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's settled, I better\ngo sign the lease right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back, guys, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we'll go with you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... you two stay right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you guys want to\nbe alone for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For god's sake, that Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:33.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's rather chilly\nfor a room facing the southeast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:47.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're here!\NShow yourself at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:06.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This place is mine, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:13.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Why are you\ndoing such a terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:26.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay\nright there... don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, why won't the door open?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:55.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you fool, for\nrefusing to heed my warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:09.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Resign yourself to the\njudgment of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're an Earth Spirit, 3rd Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:32.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I never thought someone in\nthis dimension would recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that your powers\nhave weakened considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:40.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you.\NYou must return to the earth at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:45.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That body of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I shall claim for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:09.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Such power...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be...\nImpossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess 1st Class, 2nd Category,\NUnlimited License...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you care to explain, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please... please forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:33.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he'd possessed you, it would've\ntaken three days to exorcise him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:40.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is known as an Earth Spirit, 3rd Class.\NNormally, one who controls the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:47.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since a stake was driven into my\NEarth Power Line, I lost my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:51.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you've been terrorizing\nthe occupants of this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To force them to move out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An Earth Power Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:00.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the path traveled by an Earth Spirit,\nas well as his power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If this route is severed,\nthe Earth Spirit weakens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:06.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and in some cases the land\nitself is destroyed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really... so that's what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:14.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the Earth Power Line is restored,\nthen will you resume your former duties?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to you on my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use some of the energy\nfrom the Earth Power Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:28.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Transform the Earth Power Line into an\namplifier... let my powers be multiplied!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shift the Earth Power Line at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you, Lady Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:48.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in trouble,\ndo not hesitate to summon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:51.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, a friend of mine\nwill be moving in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:54.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:58.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, you may take\non your chosen form...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:01.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving Megumi in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sign the lease?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:12.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:17.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can start college without\nany worries. Right, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, since this place\nis close to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I just can't wait until spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:24.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said ''close to school''...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:27.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, which college\nare you going to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Nekomi Institute of Technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:31.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:32.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Nekomi Institute of Technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:39.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm going to be a\nfreshman at your school this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll all be\ntogether at school, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it looks that way. I'm\ncounting on you to look out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be my senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:57.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:12.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:24.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:33.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:40.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:47.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:50.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:55.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
